claim.claim-text:
A vehicle system for scheduling media system use, the system comprising:
a vehicle computer configured to:
receive information establishing a schedule for using multiple media systems in a vehicle;
store the schedule in memory;
monitor a clock to determine when to transmit use instructions for at least one media system in the vehicle according to the media system use schedule; and
transmit the use instructions based on the media system use schedule and a clock status to one or more of the multiple media systems, wherein use of the multiple media systems is enabled in accordance with the media system use schedule.

The vehicle system of claim 8 wherein the vehicle is further configured to:
output a menu of standard media systems available in the vehicle;
receive a selection of the multiple media systems from the menu of available media system;
receive user input at the vehicle computer defining the use schedule for the multiple media systems; and
generate a media system use schedule for media system use based on the media system selection and use schedule.
